          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the chicken is cooking, boil half a kettle</p><p>Chop the <strong>dried</strong> <strong>cranberries</strong> coarsely</p><p>Add them to a bowl and cover with enough <strong>boiled water</strong> to cover completely (this helps them become juicy and plump)</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
