          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>blanched</strong> <strong>almonds</strong> to a separate tray, drizzle them with a little <strong>olive oil</strong> and place them in the oven for 5 min or until slightly darkened in colour</p><p>Once done, remove from the oven and sprinkle with <strong>salt</strong></p><p>Leave them to cool on the tray</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/415.step-5-x200.jpg",
