          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Whilst the nuts are cooling, peel and finely chop the <strong>shallot<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong></p><p>Return the reserved pan to a medium heat, once hot, add the <strong>chopped</strong> <strong>shallot</strong></p><p>Cook for 2-3 min, then add the <strong>cooked</strong> <strong>freekeh, </strong>coating all the grains in the oil</p><p>Remove from the heat and set aside until serving</p>",
